00:22:26,571 --> 00:22:51,464
he saw those women, see these are the women who had been enticing him and dancing, etc., etc., who had lain aside their musical instruments and were sleeping, some of them with saliva pouring out of their mouths, some with their bodies wet with saliva, some grinding their teeth, some talking in their sleep, some groaning, some with gaping mouths, and some others with their clothes in disorder, revealing plainly those parts of the body which should be kept concealed for fear of shame.

214
00:22:53,503 --> 00:22:57,651
