215
00:22:58,112 --> 00:23:08,689
The large terrace of his mansion, magnificently decorated and resembling the abode of Saka, king of the gods, appeared to him as an existence, seemed to him a house in flames.

216
00:23:09,450 --> 00:23:18,684
He made the inspired utterance, alas, this is beset with obstacles, alas, it is constricted, and his mind was greatly drawn towards renunciation.

217
00:23:19,525 --> 00:23:25,576
Now, unfortunately, it stresses the business of disgust.

